t%20Mr%20Dunant%20was%20the%20maiden%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize.%5Cn%5CnThe%20idea%20for%20an%20%5C%22annual%20action%20that%20could%20take%20hold%20in%20the%20whole%20world%20...%20that%20would%20be%20a%20major%20contribution%20to%20peace%5C%22%20was%20introduced%20just%20after%20World%20War%20I%20and%20evolved%20out%20of%20the%20%5C%22Red%20Cross%20Truce,%20an%20initiative%20that%20was%20studied%20by%20an%20international%20commission%20established%20at%20the%2014th%20International%20Conference%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross.%20Its%20results,%20presented%20to%20the%2015th%20International%20Conference%20in%20Tokyo%20in%201934,%20was%20approved%20and%20having%20considered%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20truce,%20and%20its%20applicability%20across%20different%20regions%20of%20the%20world,%20the%20General%20Assembly%20of%20the%20International%20Federation%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20Societies%20(IFRC)%20asked%20the%20League%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20Societies%20(LORCS)%20to%20study%20the%20feasibility%20of%20adopting%20an%20annual%20International%20Red%20Cross%20Day.%20Two%20years%20later,%20the%20proposal%20was%20adopted%20and%20the%20first%20Red%20Cross%20Day%20was%20celebrated%20on%208%20May%201948.%20The%20official%20title%20of%20the%20day%20has%20changed%20over%20time,%20and%20it%20became%20%5C%22World%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Day%5C%22%20in%201984.%5Cn%5CnWorld%20Red%20Cross%20Day%202018%20will%20be%20celebrated%20all%20across%20the%20world%20by%20the%20National%20Societies%20affiliated%20to%20the%20ICRC%20(International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross)%22,%22created_time%22:%221525776900%22,%22from%22:%7B%22id%22:%221964462284%22,%22full_name%22:%22KIIT%20International%20MUN%22,%22profile_picture%22:%22https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/vp/f18c7bfa21f12caa34e8cfc98bca15d5/5BC14075/t51.2885-19/11232668_371372543051563_787554883_a.jpg%22,%22username%22:%22instakiitmun%22%7D%7D,%22user_has_liked%22:false,%22likes%22:%7B%22count%22:11